_view_clear Button_link VanillaReact Pager-Item Pager-Item_type_next\" autoComplete=\"off\"><span class=\"Button-Text\">next</span></a></div></div></nav></div><div class=\"content__right content__right_cols_6\" id=\"search-result-aside\" data-log-node=\"2_2j59w00f\" tabindex=\"-1\" data-layout-part=\"cr\"><div role=\"complementary\" aria-label=\"More details upon request\" class=\"serp-list serp-list_right_yes serp-list_complementary_yes\" data-reqid=\"1773212902248305-18410107707699803076-balancer-l7leveler-kubr-yp-klg-259-BAL\"><div class=\"serp-item card__narrow serp-item_card serp-item_card-has-shadow \" data-cid=\"11\" data-log-node=\"2_2j59w00g\" data-fast=\"1\" data-fast-name=\"entity_search\"><div class=\"EntityCard EntityCard_entref_0oCgtlbnc4MjI3MDcxNBgDrYZvIQ\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Details\"><div class=\"EntityCardItem EntityCard-Item\" data-entity-item=\"header\"><div class=\"Root EntityCardHeader\" id=\"CardHeader__xvxdpcdkw1143ojlrpmj9-PpRkQLR\" data-state-id=\"2_2j592\"><div class=\"CardHeader\"><div class=\"CardHeader-TitleWrapper\"><h2 class=\"CardHeader-Title Typo Typo_text_xxl Typo_line_m Typo_type_bold\">OpenClaw</h2></div></div></div></div><div class=\"EntityCardItem EntityCard-Item\" data-entity-item=\"rich-text\" data-entity-cid=\"1\"><h2 class=\"SnippetTitle EntityCardItem-Title\"><span class=\"SnippetTitle-Text\">Short information</span></h2><div class=\"Root\" id=\"EntityCardRichText__5ast7izus199o2t9tygw-PpRkQLR0\" data-state-id=\"2_2j593\"><div class=\"EntityCardRichText\"><div class=\"RichFactdown EntityCardRichText-Content EntityCardRichText-Content_unfoldableSources\"><p class=\"RichFactdown-Paragraph\">Open-source autonomous artificial intelligence personal assistant software that runs locally on user devices and integrates with messaging platforms. Originally released in November 2025 under the name Clawdbot, it was renamed Moltbot following a trademark request from Anthropic, before being renamed again to OpenClaw in early 2026.</p></div><div class=\"EntitySourceLinks EntitySourceLinks_size_medium\"><div class=\"Scroller Scroller_widthFull Scroller_sameHeight Scroller_scrollDirection_none Scroller_hasArrows Scroller_hasArrows Scroller_theme_futuris Scroller_smallerArrows EntitySourceLinks-Scroller\" data-log-node=\"2_2j59w0c-0-22\"><div class=\"Scroller-Container\"><div class=\"ArrowButton ArrowButton_direction_left ArrowButton_hidden ArrowButton_withShadows Scroller-Arrow\"></div><div class=\"Scroller-Wrap\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"Scroller-ItemsWrap\"><div class=\"EntitySourceLinks-Wrapper\"><a class=\"Link EntitySourceLinks-Link\" title=\"en.wikipedia.org\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenClaw\" data-counter=\"[&quot;b&quot;]\" data-log-node=\"2_2j59w0c-0-24\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"Favicon Favicon_size_m EntitySourceLinks-Favicon Favicon-Page0 Favicon-Page0_pos_9\" style=\"width:16px;min-width:16px;height:16px;background-size:16px;background-position-y:-144px\"></div><span class=\"EntitySourceLinks-Text\">en.wikipedia.org</span></a></div></div></div><div class=\"ArrowButton ArrowButton_direction_right ArrowButton_hidden ArrowButton_withShadows Scroller-Arrow\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"EntityCardItem EntityCard-Item\" data-entity-item=\"facts\" data-entity-cid=\"2\"><div class=\"Root\" id=\"EntityCardFacts__yqmccaa73vynyqb3tgyu-PpRkQLS\" data-state-id=\"2_2j594\"><div class=\"EntityCardFacts\"><ul class=\"KeyValue KeyValue_layout_default KeyValue_gap_l\" aria-label=\"Facts\"><li class=\"KeyValue-Row\"><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemTitle\">Released<!-- -->: </div><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemValueWrapper\"><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemValue\">2025<!-- -->, <!-- -->November, 2025</div></div></li><li class=\"KeyValue-Row EntityCardFacts-Website\"><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemTitle\">Website<!-- -->: </div><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemValueWrapper\"><div class=\"KeyValue-ItemValue\"><a theme=\"normal\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"